    {
      "id": "Bmuwwch2NNPLM9LoILr5K",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 663.7828846839341,
      "y": 4581.638671875,
      "width": 353.04803466796875,
      "height": 317.90234375,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9j",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 688546768,
      "version": 190,
      "versionNonce": 1469610800,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779823311335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When to Bring Up Caching\n    -Read-heavy workload\n    -Expensive queries\n    -High database CPU\n    -Latency requirements\n\nHow to Introduce Caching\n1. Identify the bottleneck\n2. Decide what to cache\n3. Choose your cache architecture\n4. Set an eviction policy\n5. Address the downsides",
      "fontSize": 21.193489583333335,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When to Bring Up Caching\n    -Read-heavy workload\n    -Expensive queries\n    -High database CPU\n    -Latency requirements\n\nHow to Introduce Caching\n1. Identify the bottleneck\n2. Decide what to cache\n3. Choose your cache architecture\n4. Set an eviction policy\n5. Address the downsides",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
